    "description": "Are you a skilled Consultant Physician looking for your next big career move? Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates in Tiruchirappalli offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates:\nSymbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Symbiosis Hospital Asia Pacific Associates!",
